}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "SMC 9432TX F001" is silkscreened on the back of this particular card. :"50-600734-001 REV A" and the '''SMC''' logo is silkscreened on the top of the card. The Ethernet controller in use is an '''SMC''' [[http://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/93384/000009338403000113/smsc_accton.txt offshoot of '''Standard Microsystems Corp''' (??), '''Accton''' acquired majority stake from them in 1997]] ''83C171A2QF P'' (83C171, later sold as the '''SMSC''' ['''Standard Microsystems Corp'''] LAN83C171 ['''EPIC/XF''']). :An additional (and presumably older) revision uses 83C170.
